{"2651510": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "新星掠影", "steam_appid": 2651510, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>在宇宙盡頭，你遇見的——</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>是救贖，還是毀滅？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/e02a0744d9a87c31cc0a27d672739180.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遙遠的未來——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人類早已跨越星際，文明遍佈無數星球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而在自由與繁榮之下，「犯罪」也同樣無遠弗屆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了維持秩序，星際政府推出「懸賞制度」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讓賞金獵人穿梭宇宙，追捕罪犯、換取報酬。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/9b39516169bebb142da58ecd74bdc891.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——但費蘭，還算不上什麼獵人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他只是個燃料見底、隨時會漂流宇宙的倒楣船長。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每天最大的娛樂，是對著新聞裡的高額懸賞做白日夢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直到那天——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名神秘男子「7」，從陰影中現身，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用槍，強行改寫了他的航線。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被迫同行的兩人，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段橫跨太陽系的危險旅程——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從詭譎的太空站、混亂的土衛六、</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到交易橫行的火星、荒涼沉默的地球……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/85e770395e6c0ad13bb82fc9a1570d1c.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一次次任務與逃亡之間，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >費蘭逐漸發現：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「7」的身體，遠超常人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而那份力量，來自一種禁忌存在——「新星藥劑」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >強大、危險，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也帶著無法忽視的代價。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/5f5eceb749a558fe65860cf50407b86b.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/c4dbf65f1ff73fd37dcec75ec4fb29ad.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這趟旅程，究竟是——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一場逐漸靠近的羈絆？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >還是一場無法逃離的墜落？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/881435eefd25534f5b5fc4d4f147dee4.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以選擇——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與他並肩前行，探索他深不可測的過去；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以在某個瞬間，轉身逃離這名危險的男人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但一旦選擇——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就再也無法回頭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/58aa979fe8f30fc88323d4b79fd3421f.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆玩法特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦ 分歧選擇 × 多結局</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一次選擇，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >都將影響「好感度」與「憤怒值」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >並導向截然不同的結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是靠近？還是疏離？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >信任，或背叛——全由你決定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦ 賞金獵人系統</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各個星球接取懸賞任務，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >賺取資金、補充燃料，才能繼續前行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這不只是戀愛——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也是一場關於「生存」的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/fd1c8791ceaa748cb7928e44a0148a26.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ 精緻CG 13張（含差分100+）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ 劇情文本超過10萬字</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ 單一可攻略角色 × 高濃度情感刻畫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ 7種結局（含4大主要結局）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ 宇宙公路旅 × BL情感發展</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/bbbb48521e2e447d25d08ab3f63edff2.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>在宇宙盡頭，你遇見的——</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>是救贖，還是毀滅？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2651510/extras/e02a0744d9a87c31cc0a27d672739180.avif?t=1775622613\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遙遠的未來——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人類早已跨越星際，文明遍佈無數星球。</p><p clas